title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today’s Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses Kyler Murray’s new contract. How will it effect Lamar Jackson’s negotiations? Albert Breer shares the latest on how many games he thinks Deshaun Watson will miss. Plus, Andrew Marchand discusses the possibility of Charles Barkley broadcasting LIV golf.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
